# Rule Configuration

```json
{
  "pattern": "className=\\s*[\"'](mdc:[^\"']*)[\"']",
  "order": [
    "flex|grid|block|inline|inline-block|hidden",
    "relative|absolute|fixed|sticky",
    "w-|h-|p-|m-|space-",
    "overflow-|overflow-x-|overflow-y-",
    "font-",
    "text-",
    "leading-|tracking-",
    "bg-",
    "border-",
    "rounded-",
    "shadow-",
    "opacity-",
    "cursor-|pointer-events-|select-",
    "hover:|focus:|active:|disabled:"
  ],
  "message": "Tailwind classes should be ordered: Layout > Typography > Visual > Interactive > States"
}
```

# Order Categories

1. Layout
   - Display utilities (flex, grid, block)
   - Position (relative, absolute)
   - Box model (w-, h-, p-, m-)
   - Overflow

2. Typography
   - Font family and size
   - Text properties
   - Line height and spacing

3. Visual
   - Background
   - Border
   - Rounded corners
   - Shadow
   - Opacity

4. Interactive
   - Cursor
   - Pointer events
   - User select

5. States
   - Hover
   - Focus
   - Active
   - Disabled
